Tool

NameExport Shapes
ID4
AuthorO.Conrad (c) 2008

Description

The "OGR Vector Data Export" module exports vector data to various file formats using the "Geospatial Data Abstraction Library" (GDAL) by Frank Warmerdam. For more information have a look at the GDAL homepage: http://www.gdal.org GDAL Version:2.2.3 Following vector formats are currently supported:
